This is your new Play application
=====================================

This file will be packaged with your application, when using `play dist`.


PROJECT SETUP
=============

1. Download and unzip play-2.2.6.zip in folder with full privilegies

2. Edit .bashrc file and add play to the path, like: 

	PATH=$PATH:$HOME/src/java/play-2.2.6

3. Go projects directory and create an new application:

	play new rmts

4. Go the the application directory:

	cd rmts

5. Run play console:

	play

6. Setup the project to run in your favorite IDE, like Eclipse:

	eclipse

7. Import your project into eclipse.


